{"content": "<p>Minting of the <a href=\"https://www.mintedbook.com\">Minted Book</a> begins at <strong><strong>2pm PST Friday 29th April.</strong></strong></p><p><strong><strong>Official </strong>MINT Site</strong><br /><a href=\"https://www.mintedbook.com/minted-book-nft/?utm_campaign=MintFace&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=Revue%20newsletter\">https://www.mintedbook.com/minted-book-nft/</a><br /><br /><strong>Minted Hardcover NFT Deed</strong><br />Price: 0.1 eth <br />Supply 690<br />Utility: Redeem for 2 physical books (includes 100+ NFT artworks)<br /><br /><strong>Minted Digital NFT Deed</strong><br />Price: 0.03 eth <br />Supply 6,900<br />Utility: Redeem for 1 digital book (includes 100+ NFT artworks)</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/04/IMG_1089-5.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/04/IMG_1089-5.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/04/IMG_1089-5.jpg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/04/IMG_1089-5.jpg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/04/IMG_1089-5.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p><strong><strong>Share the time</strong></strong><br />🕑 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1519897148477042689?s=20&amp;t=mt4AmyNVTc-ArgTNo2rgrw&amp;utm_campaign=MintFace&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=Revue%20newsletter\">Tweet the 2pm PST 4/29 time</a> so your frens don’t miss out.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🚨Minted book opens 2pm PST Friday 29th April🚨<br /><br />OFFICIAL SITE: <a href=\"https://t.co/PBnpYIrU9M\">https://t.co/PBnpYIrU9M</a><br /><br />📔Minted Hardcover NFT Deed<br />Price: 0.1 Ξ<br />Supply 690<br />Utility: Redeem for 2️⃣physical books<br /><br />👩‍💻Minted Digital NFT Deed<br />Price: 0.03 Ξ<br />Supply 6,900<br />Utility: Redeem for 1️⃣ digital book<br /><br />1/2</p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1519897148477042689?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 29, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p><strong><strong>See what featured artists are saying</strong></strong><br />😁<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1519186973059350528?s=20&amp;t=oM_FxcNWpXnVEY4dPjZQkA&amp;utm_campaign=MintFace&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=Revue%20newsletter\">Watch artists unbox</a> the Minted book <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1519186973059350528?s=20&amp;t=oM_FxcNWpXnVEY4dPjZQkA&amp;utm_campaign=MintFace&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=Revue%20newsletter\">on Twitter</a>!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Excited to receive my Minted Book by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> featuring artist from around the world with my photography on a gorgeous double page spread. Mint for your physical and digital copy… details below 🙌🎉 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFTCommunity?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NFTCommunity</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/w3i3yIik2c\">https://t.co/w3i3yIik2c</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/gAIUvlar71\">pic.twitter.com/gAIUvlar71</a></p>&mdash; Mr Jon Kane 🔥 (@mrjonkane) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mrjonkane/status/1519789275201433600?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 28, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p><strong>🍒 Alpha for MintFace subscribers. </strong><br />If the site gets overloaded, you can use these direct links:<br />📔 <a href=\"https://physical.mintedbook.com/?utm_campaign=MintFace&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=Revue%20newsletter\">https://physical.mintedbook.com</a><br />👩‍💻<a href=\"https://digital.mintedbook.com/?utm_campaign=MintFace&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=Revue%20newsletter\">https://digital.mintedbook.com</a></p><p>Good luck on mint and thank you for supporting the art of 84 artists selected for the Minted book.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.mintedbook.com/tag/artists/\">View Minted book artists</a><br /><a href=\"https://discord.gg/7BtUVG4YE3\">Join Discord</a><br /><a href=\"https://www.mintedbook.com/oncyber-gallery/\">View OnCyber Gallery</a><br /><a href=\"https://www.mintedbook.com/smart-contract/\">View Smart Contract</a> (on Manifold)</p><hr />"}